text: Dušan Mavec (born 23 October 1947) is a Slovenian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Yugoslavia Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sežana
